Abstufung 10%

#16bae7 Hellblau

#000000 Schwarz Schriftfarbe Headlines
Abstufung: 50 % und 25% für Flächen

#707070 Dklgrau Schriftfarbe 

Verwendete Fonts

Roboto Condensed Bold
Roboto Condensed Regular
Inter Regular
Inter Bold

h1 – Roboto Condensed Bold, size: 32pt, Line-height: 32pt, #000000
h2 – Roboto Condensed Bold, size: 24pt, line-height: 24pt #000000
h3 – Roboto Condensed Regular, size: 24pt, line-height: 24pt; #16bae7 Hellblau
h4 – Roboto Condensed Regular, size: 24pt, line-height: 24pt; #afca0b Hauptfarbe Lindgrün
p (normal) – Inter Regular, size: 14pt, line-height: 17 pt, Abstand nach: 10 pt,  #707070
p (Anmerkung) – Inter Regular, size: 9pt, line-height: 11 pt,  #707070
a (im Text)- Inter Bold, size: 14 pt, line-height: 17 pt; (am Ende des Links ↗ U+2197 einfügen)
a (im Menü/Footer)- Inter Bold, size: 14 pt, line-height: 17 pt; (am Beginn des Links → U+2192 und Leerzeichen einfügen)
a:hover,  a:focus – text-decoration: underline thin dotted
